title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Dec 1 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Dec 1 2021
description:
Huge day at the Supreme Court: Left freaks out over abortion. Buck declares, "I think this is a moment where you gotta ask yourself, if we don't conserve life, what are we conserving?" CNBC's Cramer calls for military-enforced vaccine mandate -- C&B are appalled. CNN suspends Cuomo, clings to fiction they call journalism. Will Chris be "Toobined" or cut free for good? Psaki: GOP wants to stop us from saving lives. Covid latest. Clay: "The idea of 100 percent vaccination doesn't change anything."
